						<p>On the east wall of the Āñjanēya shrine in the Veṅkaṭaramaṇasvāmin temple.</p>						

						<p>The record is dated <hi rend="italic">[Bhā]va, Kārttika,</hi> śu. 12 (Written in late characters).</p>						

						<p>Damaged and indistinct. Seems to record some gift of lands to god Chinttalarāya of Tāṁḍiparati by Kṛishṇamarājulaṁgāru.</p>						

